Shield of the Storm		KEY:Path of the Storm Herald ~ Shield of the Storm	CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Barbarian Class Feature.Path of the Storm Herald.SpecialQuality.Class Feature		DESC:While you are raging, allies within your aura gain the benefits of your Storm Soul feature.
Raging Storm			KEY:Path of the Storm Herald ~ Raging Storm			CATEGORY:Special Ability		TYPE:Barbarian Class Feature.Path of the Storm Herald.SpecialQuality.Class Feature		DESC:Desert. The ground around you becomes like shifting sand. Any enemy that attempts to move more than 5 feet per turn on the ground while in your aura must make a Strength saving throw (DC %1). On a failed save, the creature's speed drops to 0 until the start of its next turn.|8+Proficiency_Bonus+CON|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Storm Herald Choice ~ Desert	DESC:Sea. Roaring winds tear through the area around you. Any creature in your aura that you hit with an attack must make a Strength saving throw (DC %1) or be knocked prone.|8+Proficiency_Bonus+STR|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Storm Herald Choice ~ Sea	DESC:Tundra. The air around you coldly slows your foes. The area within your aura is difficult terrain for your enemies.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Storm Herald Choice ~ Tundra

